column5: Anyone catch it? Best card I've seen in the longest time
Edgar ( i think it was him ) got his nose busted with a running knee, gruesome. Lots of action from what I saw. Of course this is the one I ddint watch.
Yes it was a great night of fights. I liked watching hunt knock out kongo. Rampage looked really slow and sluggish.
Agreed rampage looked like he ran a marathon before the fight.
